<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1089880-is-this-book-worth-reading-if-you-don-t">Is this book worth reading if you don&#39;t question the existence of evolution and (working in a subfield of biology) know its core principles?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1089880'><a id="like_count_community_question_1089880" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1089880?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">5 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F6117055-the-greatest-show-on-earth">like</a></span>

