              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17636804745211356827">Another great book by Richard Dawkins. This is a wonderful book that richly describes, in immense details, the wonder that is evolution. Here is a book that really shows the awe of science, and nature and how the world has become the great cornucopia of life that it has become. </span>

          </span>
