          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Why would an all-powerful creator decide to plant his carefully crafted species on islands and continents in exactly the appropriate pattern to suggest, irresistibly, that they had evolved and dispersed from the site of their evolution?&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
